There are modified XSL stylesheets for PDF publishing.
  - demo/pdf5 ... AnntenaHouse pdf5 plugin.
    - see notices directory for lisence term.
    - support FOP as xsl-fo formatter.
      - use property pdf.formatter to choose FOP(fop) or XSL Formatter(ah)
    - added customize for confidential specsheets.

  - demo/fo ... Idiom pdf2 plugin.
    - come with DITA-OT 1.5.4
    - added customize for confidential specsheets.
    - change japanese font to windows standards(MS Mincho/Gothic)
    - change FOP config to search MS Mincho/Gothic on Mac OS X
      - you need Microsoft Office for Mac

  - xsl ... DITA-OT style sheets
    - come with DITA-OT 1.5.4
    - not modified yet.

You can get original pdf5 plugin and documents from following URL.
  http://www.antenna.co.jp/XSL-FO/sample/XSLSample.htm#DITA

You can get DITA-OT from following URL.
  http://dita-ot.sourceforge.net/
